  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this research is to determine whether the prevalence of osteoporosis is
      greater in patients who suffer from Chronic obstructive pulmonary disease (COPD) or Asthma
      disease and uses inhaled steroids.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
